text: The iPad (10th generation) known as (iPad 10 and iPad 10.9-inch) is a tablet computer developed by Apple inc. It announced on October 18, 2022, It released on October 26, 2022. It runs iPadOS 16. ==Colors== iPad 10 has a four color such as blue, silver, red and yellow. ==Features== iPad 10 has a 10.9 inch Liquid Retina IPS-LCD screen, It has a USB-C. it works with the Apple Pencil. ==Other websites== * ==References== Category:IPad
title: IPad (10th generation)
